## ⚡ Differentiators Summary — Why This Stands Out

| Feature | Typical Submission | Our Approach |
|---------|-------------------|--------------|
| **Architecture** | Simple RAG vs "Agentic" (vague) | Naive RAG vs **Corrective RAG** (research-backed, specific) |
| **Dataset** | Single dataset, 1,000 queries | **Dual dataset** (NQ + HotpotQA), 1,500 queries, difficulty tiers |
| **Metrics** | Accuracy + F1 only | **12+ metrics** across retrieval, generation, operations |
| **Evaluation** | Just quantitative | **Hybrid**: Quantitative + RAGAS + LLM-as-a-Judge |
| **Analysis** | Aggregate scores only | **Failure mode taxonomy** + statistical significance |
| **Cost tracking** | None | **Per-query dollar cost** and token usage |
| **Reproducibility** | Hardcoded | **Config-driven** with checkpointing and seeding |
| **Visualization** | 1-2 basic charts | **12 chart types** + interactive Streamlit dashboard |
| **Agent Design** | Blackbox | **Component-level tracing** (per-node analysis) |
| **Report** | Brief summary | **Publication-grade** with appendix & sample outputs |

